## 1. ProfileLayoutCanvas.jsx (Owner's Edit Mode)
**File**: `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\ProfilePage\components\ProfileLayoutCanvas.jsx`

### Component Structure
This is the main canvas for rendering and editing widgets in MyProfile. It handles:

#### Pinned Widgets (Section-attached)
```jsx
<div className="profile-section-pinned-widgets">
  {pinnedWidgetsBySection[section.id]?.map((widget) => (
    <div 
      key={widget.id}
      data-widget-id={widget.id}
      className={`profile-widget-card profile-widget-size-${widget.size || 'md'} 
                  ${showLayoutBuilder ? 'is-editing is-pinned' : 'is-pinned'} 
                  ${activeWidgetId === widget.id ? 'is-widget-active' : ''}`}
      style={{
        minHeight: Number.isFinite(widget?.height) ? `${widget.height}px` : undefined,
        backgroundColor: widget.bg_color || undefined
      }}
      draggable={showLayoutBuilder}
    >
```

#### Floating Widgets (Free-positioned)
Two rendering states:
- **Edit Mode** (`showLayoutBuilder === true`):
```jsx
<div className={`profile-widget-card profile-widget-size-${widget.size || 'md'} 
                is-editing ${draggingWidgetId === widget.id ? 'is-dragging' : ''}`}
     style={{
       left: `${Number.isFinite(widget?.x) ? widget.x : 0}px`,
       top: `${Number.isFinite(widget?.y) ? widget.y : 0}px`,
       width: Number.isFinite(widget?.width) ? `${widget.width}px` : undefined,
       minHeight: Number.isFinite(widget?.height) ? `${widget.height}px` : undefined,
       backgroundColor: widget.bg_color || undefined
     }}
>
```

- **View Mode** (`showLayoutBuilder === false`):
```jsx
<div className={`profile-widget-card profile-widget-size-${widget.size || 'md'} 
                ${editingWidgetId === widget.id ? 'is-view-editing' : ''} 
