### VisitProfile Class Names
**Widget Classes:**
- `visited-profile-widget-card` - Main widget container
- `visited-profile-widget-canvas` - Floating widgets container
- `visited-profile-section-pinned-widgets` - Pinned widgets section
- `visited-profile-widget-title` - Widget title
- `visited-profile-widget-image` - Widget image
- `visited-profile-widget-note` - Widget note
- `is-pinned` - When pinned to section
- `profile-section-size-${size}` - Size variant

**Block Classes:**
- `visited-profile-widget-block-canvas` - Block canvas
- `visited-profile-widget-block` - Individual block
- `visited-profile-widget-block-${type}` - Block type indicator
- `visited-profile-widget-block-text` - Text block
- `visited-profile-widget-block-image` - Image block
- `visited-profile-widget-block-title` - Block title
- `visited-profile-widget-block-image` - Block image
- `visited-profile-widget-block-note` - Block note
- `visited-profile-widget-block-widget_card` - Widget card block (special type)

**Expanded Modal Classes:**
- `visited-profile-widget-overlay` - Overlay backdrop
- `visited-profile-widget-expanded` - Expanded modal container
- `visited-profile-widget-expanded-header` - Header section
- `visited-profile-widget-expanded-title` - Title in expanded view
- `visited-profile-widget-expanded-close` - Close button
- `visited-profile-widget-expanded-body` - Content area
- `visited-profile-widget-expanded-image` - Expanded image
- `visited-profile-widget-expanded-note` - Expanded note

