## Summary of Rendering Differences

| Feature | MyProfile | VisitProfile |
|---------|-----------|--------------|
| **Editing** | Full inline editing | Read-only |
| **Dragging** | Full drag support | Click to expand |
| **Resizing** | Full resize handles | No resize |
| **Layout Building** | `ProfileLayoutCanvas` with full controls | Inline static rendering |
| **Widget Expansion** | Inline edit panel | Modal overlay with animation |
| **Block Interaction** | Drag, resize, edit | Click to expand sub-modal |
| **Class Prefix** | `profile-` | `visited-profile-` |
| **Container Type** | Positioned absolutely | Positioned absolutely (read-only) |
